02) United States gave 7,2 million dollars for Russian ice.<br />
03) An English white stone building was ordered to be built.<br />
04) Second Asian emperor who succeeded his half brother.<br />
05) West and East artificial Chinese lakes were constructed.<br />
06) When this Portuguese king died, only his daughter was alive.<br />
